mself through college and found success in the Army, in business, and finally in teaching.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aChildrenzHaitixSocial conditions. 0aHaitian AmericansvBiography. 7aBIOGRAPHY & AUTOBIOGRAPHY / General.2bisacsh1 aCadet, Cynthia Nassano, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Texas Press Complete eBook-Package Pre-2000z978311074535140uhttps://doi.org/10.7560/71202740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780292795327423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780292795327/original  a978-3-11-074535-1  University of Texas Press Complete eBook-Package Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles